âš™ï¸ Setup Instructions

1. Clone the Repository
git clone https://github.com/Abhinandsuresh10/LocalMarket.git
cd LocalMarket

2. Install Dependencies

Frontend:

cd frontend
npm install


Backend:

cd backend
npm install


Git Contribution Workflow

1. git pull origin develop

2. git checkout -b feature/auth-system

3. git add .
   git commit -m "Added JWT auth system"

4. git push origin feature/auth-system


